summary: An ordinance appropriating the sum of $150.00 from the general fund of the City of Seattle, to pay the claim of Ida Sackett for personal injuries received by said Ida Sackett on the 22nd day of September, 1917, at about 4:30 P.M. while walking on the sidewalk nearly in front of 6245 Flora Avenue, Seattle, and authorizing the drawing of a warrant therefor.
